{"tid":2078413,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"日本出咗極高汁光服fashion!! 你今日光服左香港未??","createTime":"2020-06-25T04:39:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T10:59:14.000Z","uid":74888,"like":11,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b8df4a200b09b2977dc578b46be30ed70a428d1e","tid":2078413,"uid":74888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T04:39:08.000Z","msg":"各位連登仔你地好，我哋係一班喺日本嘅手足 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話咁快就一年，相信抗爭已經成為咗咁多位連登仔生活嘅一部份<br />\n<br />\n但你地又有無諗過一件Tee都可以成為行動文宣，時刻提醒自己抗爭仲係進行中呢？<br />\n<br />\n我地係一班來自日本嘅手足同設計師，攪左壇叫「光服香港」嘅Project，Design咗5款日系設計嘅Tee，仲充滿彩蛋，識日文的話可以慢慢研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隱侮嘅設計，可以俾大家日日將抗爭「穿」喺日常生活當中。唔方便嗌口號嘅場合都可以著返件低調啲嘅TEE，大家手足，心照。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w1BqtQx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw1BqtQx.png&h=7ba4cf47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QMZznax.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQMZznax.jpg&h=2459fcfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uSd4KoT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuSd4KoT.jpg&h=083912b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次Project部份嘅收益將會捐比612同其他抗爭基金支持香港手足，一小部份會留返黎打日本戰線跪求大家多多支持，大大力懲罰!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【內有多圖】歡迎大家到撳入去以下Crowdfunding網大力懲罰我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://igg.me/at/DDDDDHKtee2020\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Figg.me%2Fat%2FDDDDDHKtee2020&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfSC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=54578918\" target=\"_blank\">https://igg.me/at/DDDDDHKtee2020</a><br />\n<br />\n2樓係FAQ, 大家有疑問可以睇一睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2460053fc0e61c69352a2244355325fb55263abd","tid":2078413,"uid":74888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T04:43:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">常見問題FAQ </span><br />\n<br />\nFrequently Asked Questions <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>T-shirt 的製作物料是？ </strong><br />\n請瀏覽眾籌頁面的「產品詳情」部份。Please refer to the &ldquo;Product Details&rdquo; section.<br />\n<strong>洗衣時有什麼注意事項？</strong><br />\n建議內外反轉，如一般T恤般清洗。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>有哪些尺寸？</strong><br />\n請瀏覽眾籌頁面的「Our Design」部份<br />\n<br />\n<strong>可不可更換尺碼？</strong><br />\n眾籌完結後不可更換尺碼<br />\n<br />\n<strong>如下單後發現錯誤訂購怎辦？</strong><br />\n請盡快聯絡我們，於眾籌完結後不可更改<br />\n<br />\n<strong>之後能否追加訂單？</strong><br />\n感謝你對我們產品的愛戴，如需加單，請直接再訂購。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>能否大量訂購？</strong><br />\n如訂購20件以上，請直接聯絡我們。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>什麼時候到貨？</strong><br />\n我們會根據落單次序發貨，預計8至9月送出，貨品有機會分批寄出<br />\n<br />\n<strong>日後能否透過其他途徑購買</strong><br />\n我們正積極考慮中，請密切留意ActwithHK的Facebook專頁。<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/actwithhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Factwithhk&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfSC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=99953982\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/actwithhk</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>海外居民購買會否有其他額外費用？例如稅款。</strong><br />\n不會，但郵寄費用會有差別。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>如果被海關扣關，可以怎樣處理？</strong><br />\n請自行與海關聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>捐款及支出等資料會否公開？</strong><br />\n眾籌完結後會以眾籌報告形式電郵予支持本項目人士<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>海外居民購買會否有其他額外費用？</strong><br />\n不會，但郵寄費用會有差別。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>如被海關徵收稅款，該如何處理？</strong><br />\n請購買者自行處理，但在一般情況下不會被徵收關稅。"},{"pid":"be7b805ed0ecf7c01ac980d6903e6664ceda9edf","tid":2078413,"uid":282352,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T04:46:17.000Z","msg":"整件衫加幾粒外國字又想吮錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我又扮下俄仔手足,求其加幾粒俄文又可以食饅頭,仲有法文德文etc<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1be86d860e8d30aa84ff532e085a0eb8d2b470fb","tid":2078413,"uid":169071,"like":2,"